@Comment:	mealtime is about 10.5 minutes long. All things considered , this isn't too terribly disfunctional an outing. Apparently this is the second try , since there were technical difficulties before. Chi is sometimes resistant , occasionally cooperative. Mot says <come on> and <let's go> perhaps more times than CLAN can count. Chi recites a few dreary sayings <no one's perfect in the world> and <I know the world ain't fun with games>. Most of the tape is arguing between Chi and Mot , about eating and about the tape.
